high_descs: Turn right to face the cabinet under the right loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up the tea pot from the cabinet under the right loaf of bread.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Wash the tea pot in the sink and remove it.
Take a step to the left and look down to face the left most cabinet.
Place the tea pot in the left most cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: TO wash a tea pot and put it in the left most cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step, the face the left counter.
Take the kettle out of the cabinet under the counter, the one that's in between the two loaves of bread.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Place the kettle in the bottom left shelf, in front of the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean kettle in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to face the rightmost loaf of bread on the countertop.
Take the tea kettle out of the cabinet directly below the rightmost loaf of bread.
Turn left to walk to the sink.
Rinse the tea kettle in the sink.
Turn left to face the spatula on the counter.
Put the tea kettle away in the cabinet directly below the spatula on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tea kettle to put away in a cabinet.
